Pre-Game Insights: Australia entered the semis on a seven-match unbeaten streak.
South Africa have had their number over Australia in the group stages early on in the tournament.
South Africa were schooled by India later on in the group stages but came back stronger in their final league game against Afghanistan.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The ICC World Cup 2023 semifinal game between Australia and South Africa will be played on Thursday, November 16, 2023.
The semifinal match between Australia and South Africa will be played at the Eden Gardens in Kolkata.
The ICC ODI World Cup 2023 semifinal between Australia and South Africa is scheduled to start at 2:00 p.m. IST. (+5:30 GMT)
The live streaming of the ODI World Cup Semifinal between Australia and South Africa will be on Disney+ Hotstar.
